These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip, daisy, poppy
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, skydiving, gardening, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the colombian is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the indonesian is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growspoppy##2
3. the colombian is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Flower   | tulip | poppy   | bellflower  | daisy  |
| Hobby   | skydiving    | woodworking    | board-games      | gardening    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

