.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, azalea, sunflower, orchid
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, artichoke, papaya
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the person eating papaya is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person eating papaya and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
9. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Flower         | orchid | azalea    | sunflower  | poppy    |
| Food   | cauliflower      | garlic  | papaya  | artichoke |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

