.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, d&b, pop, trance
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, pink, orange, blue
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person who likes orange is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who likes pink is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the fan of soul is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fan of pop and the person who likes pink##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre        | d&b | pop     | soul   | trance     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Color         | black   | orange | blue       | pink    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

