.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ebony, azure, fuchsia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, tiparillo, blend, bongani
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes azure is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person who likes ebony is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the bongani-smoker and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Color           | azure | fuchsia | aquamarine    | ebony     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Cigar         | fonseca     | blend       | bongani | tiparillo |

