.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, go, scrabble
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, dutch, russian
City: rome, new-york, prague, hannover
 1. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is the dutch##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the dutch and the person traveling to prague##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the argentine is the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing go##1
10. the dutch is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game   | go | mah-jongg | whist  | scrabble  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| City     | rome    | hannover   | new-york    | prague  |

