4 different games are played: monopoly, bridge, domino, mah-jongg
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, quad-bike, subway
1. the oliveros-smoker is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the car##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the bluemaster-smoker##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is the vegafina-smoker##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | water   | iced-tea    | juice  |
| Cigar   | vegafina    | oliveros   | bluemaster | montecristo |
