.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, spinach, tomato
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, hedgehog, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, metal
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, bike, train
 1. the person eating lettuce is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person eating tomato is the person driving the bike##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the fan of metal is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the rabbit and the person driving the quad-bike##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| Pet           | rabbit | lizard | goldfish   | hedgehog |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | folk       | metal      | house     |
| Transport         | bike       | train | quad-bike    | bus  |

