 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is the person who likes amber##1
 5. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person who growssunflower and the person who growszinnia##2
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who growssunflower and the person who growszinnia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Color   | amber    | pink    | azure      | red |
