 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person who growstulip##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
